Package org.shared.fft

A package for FFTs.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cacheable
    Marks an array as being suitable for having its FFT cached.
    FftService
    Defines a Service for FFT operations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConvolutionCache
    A specialization of FftCache for RealArrays and ComplexArrays.
    FftCache<C extends AbstractArray<C,C,R,?>,R extends AbstractArray<R,C,R,?>>
    A class for thread-safe caching of padded and FFT'd convolution kernels.
    FftOps
    A class of mixed-radix FFT operations in support of JavaFftService.
    JavaFftService
    An FftService implementation in pure Java.
    ModalFftService
    An FftService backed by a service provider as well as a pure Java implementation.
